com.plexobject.rx.impl

Class ObservableDelegate<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.plexobject.rx.impl.ObservableDelegate<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of subscription data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable<T>

    public class ObservableDelegate<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observable<T>
    This is implementation of Observable that uses user-specified consumer function to notify subscriber for data and errors
